{"tid":687213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓男偕洋女開房打爛花瓶　同職員拗數掃興收場","createTime":"2018-06-02T04:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T11:25:04.000Z","uid":122,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6574505700bf8c01155200d20b0c7b4ef2795bfa","tid":687213,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"開房打爛花瓶，韓男掃興賠錢。一名30歲韓國籍姓金男子，凌晨4時許，在尖沙咀一間酒吧消遣後，偕同一名18歲新相識芬蘭籍少女，返回麼地道32-48號麗東大廈一間賓館擬共度春宵，惟少女疑飲醉酒，情緒激動，在接待處打爛一個價值約100港元的花瓶，職員遂要求賠償，惟雙方發生爭拗，少女繼而奪門離開賓館，衝落樓下，金尾隨追回時，雙方在街頭發生拉扯。 <br />\n<br />\n與此同時，警方接報趕至調查，了解事件始末後，金願意向賓館賠償損失，而少女在路邊接受救護員檢查期間，遇上途經現場的友人，事後由友人接回，毋須送院。金以為遇上「飛來蜢」，沒想到結局是賠了金錢掃興收場。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/WeakAgileAustraliancattledog-max-1mb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FWeakAgileAustraliancattledog-max-1mb.gif&h=17336949&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87693c69426fdd387266e8d9ae60ff496c240100","tid":687213,"uid":20291,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:08:17.000Z","msg":"泡菜狗係香港食<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">荷蘭</span></span>白虎&middot;仲要18歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756eb3db98027b90f7115862b63ba24d148e47aa","tid":687213,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:10:45.000Z","msg":"100蚊同芬蘭少女"},{"pid":"0548bb6ced4f38584f2459ef8c732d6a39e237be","tid":687213,"uid":37297,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"87693c69426fdd387266e8d9ae60ff496c240100","tid":687213,"uid":20291,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:08:17.000Z","msg":"泡菜狗係香港食<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">荷蘭</span></span>白虎&middot;仲要18歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,